metadata.name: MIROHERE #1/69
metadata.description:
This art may or may not be a legend.

V.1.0 / 18.04.2023  
Big artwork on the occasion of my 2 year anniversary in NFT! Everything that surrounded me and inspired me in one canvas! This work is meant to be never ending. I will be refining it, adding new events and episodes from the world of crypto and NFT.

V.1.0.1 / 20.04.2023  
- Now we know what Beeple is whispering in Nakamigos' ear.  
- Make memcoins great again!  
It's impossible to miss the start of cryptocurrency meme season.  
$PEPE is already breathing down the back of $DOGE.
